      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Common risks generally involve title issues, such as uncovering previously undisclosed liens or encumbrances on the property. There can also be delays in inspections or financing, which might cause disagreements about the closing timeline. Less commonly, there's a risk of miscommunication regarding the final required documentation, which could stall the fund release.",
